Interface DelegatePurpose

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.dnd.DropOption, net.proteusframework.core.locale.NamedObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEntityDelegatePurpose, DefaultDelegatePurpose, SimpleDelegatePurpose

    public interface DelegatePurpose
extends net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.dnd.DropOption
    Identifies the purpose of the delegating data.

    For persistence of static purposes, implementations should provide a static valueOf(String) method that returns an instance based on the name.

    Author:
    Ben Barber (bbarber@i2rd.com)
